{"tid":1498214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"成立「國際人士組成既監警會」 。大家唔好中計，特別係警察。","createTime":"2019-08-23T10:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T13:16:35.000Z","uid":103718,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae20892dd2f23bbbc65c583cff759e2fe6aca93","tid":1498214,"uid":103718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"成立「國際人士組成既監警會」 <br />\n<br />\n好似好中立。 成員全部係政府搵，會搵咩人係一個大疑問。 點知果個人係唔係中立？<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係，點解政府一直唔肯成立獨立調查？只係要監警做野？<br />\n<br />\n因為獨立調查係會將成件事由頭到尾去睇去查，理論上要查特首等高官。但監警會呢？只會局限於查警察！即係點啊？即係擺警察上枱，係成個警隊比人查，查完等黃絲下左火就算，政府高官唔洗負責任啊！"},{"pid":"9cfe9ed53f99716619e4ab9695af3fca1132b1fb","tid":1498214,"uid":294,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"主席奶共仲有咩好中立<br />\n<br />\n立法會咪又係死，更何況監警會"},{"pid":"79a81da2fc223233be7796c3b556bce85415f9bc","tid":1498214,"uid":140552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"支那一個 北韓一個 伊朗又一個 俄狗又一個都四個了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9cea82910cabeb60fda69923150a1e6d4da40f","tid":1498214,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"無人中計"},{"pid":"8365abf57a55096d490632f3a18905575ab70a1c","tid":1498214,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"只要睇班狗的反應就知信唔信得過<br />\n班狗唔反枱=信唔過"},{"pid":"2365d7f0ca6d7038d9d55cfcebe58b5d6cefe18a","tid":1498214,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ae20892dd2f23bbbc65c583cff759e2fe6aca93","tid":1498214,"uid":103718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"成立「國際人士組成既監警會」 <br />\n<br />\n好似好中立。 成員全部係政府搵，會搵咩人係一個大疑問。 點知果個人係唔係中立？<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係，點解政府一直唔肯成立獨立調查？只係要監警做野？<br />\n<br />\n因為獨立調查係會將成件事由頭到尾去睇去查，理論上要查特首等高官。但監警會呢？只會局限於查警察！即係點啊？即係擺警察上枱，係成個警隊比人查，查完等黃絲下左火就算，政府高官唔洗負責任啊！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"國際人士不等於中立<br />\n<br />\n同埋根本監警會係自己查自己<br />\n話事嘅人全保皇<br />\n<br />\n無傳召權<br />\n查唔到幕後黑手<br />\n<br />\n絕對係騙局"},{"pid":"5dcc2b10c8a1c213371eb51e6d95670b0a85f36c","tid":1498214,"uid":245644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"唔會收貨， 要刑事追究"},{"pid":"dc50c6b839cb3380f82443615fbedce9d8601bb2","tid":1498214,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"建議解散警隊，由解放軍進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5735079ed497bbd8b0a0053c68fd4b183006ecac","tid":1498214,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會都廢<br />\n睇下鉛水 紅磡站一個都冇告就知"},{"pid":"0422915d8c80351791f15fdf3c9b8d6d39f25d78","tid":1498214,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"林鄭個仔咪英國人囉<br />\n夠唔夠國際"},{"pid":"54de54cad726341b0c40e47be22070691ead872b","tid":1498214,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國都好多鬼佬收編咗"},{"pid":"a96ea8a938ce48fe7dad1931e57f08138f0eff04","tid":1498214,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>聽日824對家吹大雞發動萬人圍港台<br />\n中共又發動宣傳機器想港台跪同清洗</strong><br />\n<br />\n營救香港電台！對家堅吹大雞萬人圍 配合國家機器滅利君雅鏗鏘集頭條新聞聲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afeaiKU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afeaiKU</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一人一信撐港台<br />\n去信廣管局</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fba_archives.ofca.gov.hk%2Fcn%2Fcontact%2F&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=4a49ace7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依個唔算投訴，咪當意見咁send<br />\n記得話港台31,32台都有睇，做得好，最like咩節目同點解<br />\n唔好太黃絲feel 同唔好用standard form<br />\n會只當一份意見</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝瀏覽我們的網址。如有任何有關廣播事務的查詢，可按以下方式與我們聯絡： <br />\n<br />\n以電子郵件方式傳送至<br />\nba@tela.gov.hk<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3faRZNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3faRZNL.jpg&h=796e8d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以書面方式寄</strong><br />\n廣播事務管理局秘書處<br />\n經影視及娛樂事務管理處<br />\n香港灣仔告士打道5號<br />\n稅務大樓39樓<br />\n(傳真號碼：(852) 2507 2219)<br />\n<br />\n致電查詢電話號碼：(852) 2594 5721"},{"pid":"beb7798f42c33f5c3c8a41c9dd0d2ebd944015e4","tid":1498214,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n監狗會認同虛設我知<br />\n但想問同獨立調查委員會有咩唔同？<br />\n我知既分別係獨立調查委員會係有權傳召證人<br />\n但想問下傳召證人既作用係咩？<br />\n同兩者重有咩分別？<br />\n屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想同屋企人解釋個重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af451a6972732b5683ce32cd6c1341c78837cf1","tid":1498214,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔中計無用，要一齊做文宣俾大眾睇"},{"pid":"a0b4fec59e6a6a367c87a3b67ffb39ab6dd4ce72","tid":1498214,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"無起訴櫂傳召權搵幾多人搵咩人都無撚用"},{"pid":"3831fa0214f098accbd4c4fbc4adb239bcdb9400","tid":1498214,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"講乜都無用<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n一係準備10.1賀國慶"},{"pid":"d6874397c6d6902e7f8f219fdac396732cc31399","tid":1498214,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a81da2fc223233be7796c3b556bce85415f9bc","tid":1498214,"uid":140552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"rep